// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0158 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8681ed1e-6814-58f8-9934-132027e1e7e5

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
